Buy "Liability" Now: https://rse.lnk.to/Liability
Subscribe for more: http://bit.ly/RhymesayersYT

"Bar Breaker" is featured on Prof's album, Liability, available on all digital and streaming platforms, as well as CD and vinyl LP: https://rse.lnk.to/Liability

Song–
Written and performed by Prof
Beat by Aesop Rock

Video–
Co-Directors: Kron & Andrew Melby
AC: Keith Moeching
Edited: Andrew Melby
Producers: Maria Malik, Jacob Anderson, & Mike Campbell
Video Crew: Sam Koshiol & Joshua Stadtherr
Bar Breaker Beauties: Chrissy Wallin, Laura Wilfer, Bailey Cogan, Yaisha Neiderhiser, Brianna Golubowicz, Brooke McDaniel, Julie Dailson, Sonya Dowd, Kiersten Stoeckel, Temira, Ellie Silverman, & Nicole Hamilton
Special Thanks: GoPro Inc, POS, Sims, Joe Synikins, Derrick Koch, Brian Denny, Turf Club, Stophouse Street Team, and everyone else who helped on the ambulance & the cut bar scenes.


#Liability #BarBreaker
